me\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantPrice\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1\u0026amp;isPreview=1\u0026amp;asins=0316565164,031649884X,0316452467,0316452564,0316452661,0316452769,0316452866,0316452963,0316453064,0316453161\u0026amp;tag=gamespot-primeday-20\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e                        \u003c/p\u003e              \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eThe box set of five novels is a great pickup during Amazon\u0026#39;s sale, but new readers should start with \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Last-Wish-Introducing-Witcher/dp/0316452467?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eThe Last Wish\u003c/a\u003e and then read \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0316452564?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eSword of Destiny\u003c/a\u003e before diving into the first novel. Both books are short story collections that take place before the events of Blood of Elves.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003eThe Last Wish and Sword of Destiny are compiled in a \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Witcher-Stories-Boxed-Set-Destiny/dp/0316565164?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003ematching paperback box set for $27 (was $35)\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Witcher-Stories-Boxed-Set-Destiny/dp/0316565164?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eThe Witcher Stories Box Set (2 Books)\u003c/a\u003e -- $27 (\u003cdel\u003e$35\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eAt this time, however, you\u0026#39;ll actually get a better deal by purchasing the collections individually in paperback.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1\u0026amp;isPreview=1\u0026amp;asins=0316565164,031649884X,0316452467,0316452564,0316452661,0316452769,0316452866,0316452963,0316453064,0316453161\u0026amp;tag=gamespot-primeday-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Witcher Series (Paperback)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003col\u003e\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Last-Wish-Introducing-Witcher/dp/0316452467?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eThe Last Wish: Introducing The Witcher\u003c/a\u003e -- $9.67 (\u003cdel\u003e$19\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0316452564?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eSword of Destiny\u003c/a\u003e -- $12.85 (\u003cdel\u003e$20\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0316452661?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eBlood of Elves\u003c/a\u003e -- $8.26 (\u003cdel\u003e$20\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Time-Contempt-Witcher-4/dp/0316452769?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eThe Time of Contempt\u003c/a\u003e -- $10.79 (\u003cdel\u003e$19\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0316452866?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eBaptism of Fire\u003c/a\u003e -- $13.31 (\u003cdel\u003e$19\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0316452963?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eThe Tower of Swallows\u003c/a\u003e -- $10.39 (\u003cdel\u003e$20\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0316453064?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eThe Lady of the Lake\u003c/a\u003e -- $13.52 (\u003cdel\u003e$20\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0316453161?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eSeason of Storms\u003c/a\u003e -- $11.87 (\u003cdel\u003e$20\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003cp\u003eSapkowski would later return to the series with \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0316453161?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eSeason of Storms\u003c/a\u003e, a prequel novel set between stories in The Last Wish. The aforementioned \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Crossroads-Ravens-Witcher-Andrzej-Sapkowski/dp/0316597732?tag=gamespot-preorders-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eCrossroads of Ravens\u003c/a\u003e, the ninth book in the series, takes place before the story collections, so it will be the first book chronologically when it releases in English on September 30. It\u0026#39;s billed as a standalone story, so it could prove to be a good starting point for new readers of Sapkowski\u0026#39;s fantasy fiction.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1\u0026amp;isPreview=1\u0026amp;asins=0316333522,0316453269,0316453366,031645155X,031645690X,0316457035,0316457132,031645723X,0316597732\u0026amp;tag=gamespot-primeday-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Witcher Series (Hardcover)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003col\u003e\u003cli dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\